<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧瞪着悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13839</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒说你可以让国王起死回生的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧说，“救救他吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看了八戒一眼。八戒忍着笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父，念紧箍咒吧！”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要！”悟空大叫道，“我去请太上老君帮忙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他做的药丸可以让人长生不老。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也许他也有让人起死回生的药丸。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太上老君正忙着做药水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>丹炉里不断地冒着蒸汽。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，悟空冲了进来，说：“你好啊，太上老君！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太上老君叹了口气说：“你来这里干什么？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69700</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你应该是在护送唐僧去西天的路上啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空在房间里到处走，翻看了所有瓶瓶罐罐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是在护送唐僧啊。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们现在在帮一个国王。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他伸手碰了碰一个蓝色瓶子。瓶子里装满了液体。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太上老君吓了一跳，说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么都别碰。告诉我你来这里干什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要一种能让人起死回生的药丸。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110146</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空说，“给我一千颗。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110147</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太上老君停下了手头的事情，走向了悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你居然敢向我要一千颗药丸！”他说，“出去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑。“我在开玩笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我并不是真的需要一千颗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>给我一百颗，我马上走。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太上老君握紧拳头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一颗都不会给你。出去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空挠了挠脑袋，装作正在思考的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想一想。我也不需要一百颗，就给我十颗吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好大的胆子！”太上老君大叫，“出去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“其实，我只需要一颗药丸。”悟空说，“给我吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“出去！”太上老君大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空叹了口气，离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太上老君回到了丹炉旁，继续搅拌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，他停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那猴子一定会回来惹麻烦的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他自言自语道，“我应该给他一颗的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太上老君打开了一个罐子，拿出了一颗药丸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走到外面，发现悟空正在等他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217194</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“又见面啦。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我正在想我要给你惹点什么麻烦好呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太上老君皱起了眉头，把药丸给了悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给你，走吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空回到了寺院。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家看着悟空把药丸放进了国王的嘴里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王全身开始发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他突然睁开了眼睛，坐了起来，看着悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你……你救了我。”国王说，“我又活过来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265028</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他转身看到了站在身边的王子。“我的儿子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265029</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“父亲！”王子说。他握住父亲的手，低头行礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很想念你。现在是您回宫的时候了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子领着所有人回到了王宫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们从卫兵面前走过，进入了正殿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子在道士面前跪下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，我的儿子。”道士说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们是什么人？”王子站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298839</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是唐僧。他要去西天佛祖那里取经。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这三位是他的徒弟。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>道士看了看站在他们身边的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那人穿着斗篷。“穿斗篷的那个人是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321022</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个人摘下帽子，露出了脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>道士大吃一惊：“国王！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空抽出了金箍棒朝着道士打下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>道士打了个响指，消失不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>